To proceed, we need to specify the expression for the 3-string vertex .
The 3-string vertex can be represented as a ket-state in the tensor product of
the three string  Fock spaces. It has the form
H_3  = P   V_F  V_B (_3  _),
where the kets  and   are constructed to satisfy
the bosonic and fermionic kinematic symmetries and  are defined 
in frame  in the Appendix.
The bosonic factor  is given by
